                    </div>
                    <span>I have roadraced for about 5 years now and have used the checklists in this book MANY times to help answer questions that I didn't even know existed within myself.  <p>Having this book handy helps since I don't always have Keith there to ask me the proper questions.  There are certainly things that should be thought out after a ride or practice session and this book HAS THE QUESTIONS to think with!!!!!   I really recommend this book to anyone who wants to ride faster and/or better through those twisty corners.<p>GREAT BOOK!<p>Stoney Landers</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Quite good technical reference</div>
